summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 80E, page 188 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in North 132' of Tract 25, south 170' of Tract 22, west 120' of south 170' of Tract 23, and north 127' of west 120' of Tract 24, all in Dunlap's Plat of Land on Lake Washington, located on both sides of Director St. from 48th Ave. So. to line 120' east of 50th Ave. So., from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
